<HEADLINE> Martin Looking for 'La Vida Calma' </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Ricky Martin is looking for a little quiet after  
the roaring success of his hit song ``Livin' La Vida Loca.'' 
</P>
