pick and the 201st pick. 
</P>
<P>
	PHOENIX COYOTES--Traded F Jim Cummins to Montreal for the 168th  
pick. 
</P>
<P>
	SAN JOSE SHARKS--Traded the 149th pick to Detroit for a  
fifth-round pick in the 2000 draft. Traded the 172nd pick to 
Vancouver for a sixth-round pick in the 2001 draft. 
</P>
<P>
	TAMPA BAY LIGHTNING--Traded the first pick to Vancouver for the  
fourth pick, obtained from Chicago, and two picks in the third 
round. Traded the No. 4 pick, obtained from Vancouver, to the New 
York Rangers for G Dan Cloutier, RW Niklas Sundstrom and first and 
third-round picks in 2000. 
</P>
<P>
	VANCOUVER CANUCKS--Traded D Bryan McCabe and its first-round pick  
in 2000 or 2001 to Chicago for the fourth pick. Traded the No. 1 
pick, obtained from Tampa Bay, to Atlanta for the No. 2 pick and a 
conditional third-round pick in 2000. 
</P>
